title: PANTERA 3 Vulgar Videos From Hell (Big Papi) MP4 1999
description:
Rated R - For language, nudity and adult situations.

I am not really a video guy. I mean Big Papi is not a video guy so forgive the larger than necessary size, but you will find the quality as good as the source DVD with stereo sound preserved. There is 4 hours of video so that could explain the overall size.

- Big Papi




A Customer wrote:

Well, what can I say? This is what every Pantera fan could ever want. All 3 videos, 4 hours of total Pantera.
Cowboys from Hell: The Videos- The shortest, but 60% of it is all music. Awesome live performance of "The Art of Shredding" and "Heresy"

Vulgar Video- 1 hour long, the FUNNIEST of all 3. Expect to crack up on most parts. It has live clips of "Domination" and "Primal Concrete Sledge"

Watch It Go- 2 full hours of Pantera. Covers footage from 1994 to 1996, but there are no live songs here.

- A real Pantera fan shouldn't be without this DVD. Hail Pantera, the Kings of all that is Metal.
